snippet.title: Outcasters - Official Launch Trailer | Now Available on Stadia
snippet.description:
Outcasters is officially here! Play it today for free with Stadia Pro! https://stadia.com/link/e9918gnitHFUdNym6

Curve your shots and be the last player standing in this adorably frenetic, fast-paced eight player combat game that tests your speed and creativity.

Outcasters is a chaotic multiplayer combat game for you and up to 8 players.

Battle your way across arenas and curve your shots to creatively defeat your opponents. With customizable Outcasters and all sorts of power-ups it’s a chaotically fun multiplayer arena game that gives a hook-shot an all new meaning. Only on Stadia.
